OL,13,     Gthe perfect alibi, but DCI
OL,14,     GTaggart is convinced he is
OL,15,     Gguilty. Meanwhile, DS Jardine
OL,16,     Ginvestigates escalating racial
OL,17,     Gattacks at a block of flats.
