OL,4,G0245FSecrets of the River Clyde
OL,5,     GThe River Clyde is one of
OL,6,     GBritain's most important rivers
OL,7,     Gwith an incredible history. It
OL,8,     Ghas been a source of wealth and a
OL,9,     Gsymbol of pride for the great
OL,10,     Gcity of Glasgow and for Scotland.
